        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>College Loan Deferment for Recovery Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to allow borrowers to defer student loans while they are enrolled in a drug treatment program and during the 30 days after completing the program.</p>]]></text>
